Habet stellas, incapite obscuras tres, in singulis humeris singulas claras, Iu dextro cubito unam, in eadem manu unam, iu medio pectore unam, in spina duas, in ventre splendidas duas, in dextro lumbo claram unam, in cauda tres, in singulis genibus retrorsus duas, in utroque armo unam, in utrisque pedibus anterioribus singulas.
